    "# Q1. Number of Elements in a Range\n",
    "\n",
    "### Question\n",
    "\n",
    "How many elements are there between **[135, 246]** (inclusive)?\n",
    "\n",
    "### Formula\n",
    "\n",
    "Number of elements = **Last − First + 1**\n",
    "\n",
    "### Calculation\n",
    "\n",
    "= 246 − 135 + 1\n",
    "\n",
    "= 111 + 1\n",
    "\n",
    "= **112**\n",
    "\n",
    "✅ **Answer: 112**"
   ]
  }
 ],
